  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Input Variants</h2>
    <p>Inputs with a <code>list</code> attribute display a dropdown arrow by default. Use <code>.no-arrow</code> to hide it, or <code>.search</code> for a search icon on the left.</p>

    <browser-window src="/docs/snippets/demos/datalist-variants.html" url="datalist-variants.html" title="Input variants" shadow></browser-window>

